# ==============================================================================
# .dockerignore — SpectraMind V50 (NeurIPS 2025 Ariel Data Challenge)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Purpose:
#   • Keep Docker build context lean (faster, reproducible, CI-safe)
#   • Mirror .gitignore + .dvcignore for consistency
#   • Exclude ephemeral data, secrets, and generated artifacts
#   • Only source code, configs, and minimal assets make it into images
# ==============================================================================

